title: Citywide Research Day set for November (Oklahoma State University - Tulsa)
text: ( Source : Oklahoma State University - Tulsa ) Thursday, October 08 , 2015 Students and faculty from OSU-Tulsa may submit posters and papers for the third Citywide Research Day on Friday, Nov. 6 . The event is open to all students and faculty
